RetroSSL Modifications
---------------------

Modifications made for Open Watcom C/C++ compatibility and Windows 98 SE 
target platform are minimal adaptations of the original BearSSL code.

This experimental project is NOT FOR PRODUCTION USE and is provided for
educational and entertainment purposes only.